description: The contract involves leasing office space in the town of Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec. The proposed space must meet specific criteria, including a lease term of approximately 10 years, a minimum of 1,652 square meters of usable office space, and 12 reserved and secured parking spaces. The proposed space must also be accessible by public transport within 500 meters of the nearest entrance to the building, and the building must be accessible to people with reduced mobility. The storage space must have a minimum height of 6 meters, be equipped with a motorized garage door, and have a landing place. Note that this is not a tender process, but rather an inquiry into the availability of space for lease.
